Bei?

562
00:34:25,470 --> 00:34:26,550
Why are you back?

563
00:34:26,590 --> 00:34:28,910
We're on break from the art school,
so I came home.

564
00:34:30,430 --> 00:34:31,300
What happened?

565
00:34:32,260 --> 00:34:33,820
