Let me see.

568
00:34:36,700 --> 00:34:37,180
Hey.

569
00:34:37,660 --> 00:34:38,660
Let me have a look.

570
00:34:43,960 --> 00:34:45,340
I'll help you put on some ointment.

571
00:34:56,950 --> 00:34:57,470
