It doesn't.

573
00:35:15,910 --> 00:35:18,550
I don't know when it started.

574
00:35:20,990 --> 00:35:23,860
All I know is that Jinrui was
my only salvation

575
00:35:25,660 --> 00:35:27,180
in Nanqiao Village.

576
00:35:27,860 --> 00:35:29,950
He was the dearest person to me.

577
00:35:39,990 --> 00:35:40,660
Jinrui.

578
00:35:41,660 --> 00:35:43,110
Have you thought more

579
00:35:43,110 --> 00:35:44,260
about grad school?

580
00:35:44,550 --> 00:35:45,630
I'm still thinking.

581
00:35:46,660 --> 00:35:47,660
You should take the exam.

582
00:35:47,720 --> 00:35:48,950
There's still two years to go.

583
00:35:49,120 --> 00:35:51,110
Plenty of time to figure out
what you want to study.

584
