love each other freely.

591
00:36:11,860 --> 00:36:13,780
That we could stay together forever.

592
00:36:14,700 --> 00:36:16,340
Mm, this flavor's still the best.

593
00:36:17,430 --> 00:36:18,660
Eat up.

594
00:36:27,700 --> 00:36:32,220
But dreams always end eventually.

595
00:36:40,070 --> 00:36:43,030
Jinrui left me.

596
00:36:44,430 --> 00:36:46,700
He never looked back.

597
00:36:47,700 --> 00:36:48,950
But I don't blame him.

598
00:36:51,070 --> 00:36:55,070
Because I know this is just my fate.

599
00:36:57,630 --> 00:36:59,070
I'm not someone who gets to be loved.

600
00:37:02,990 --> 00:37:04,360
Hey there, pretty. All alone?

601
00:37:04,360 --> 00:37:05,700
Come on, let's grab some food.

602
00:37:05,910 --> 00:37:06,470
No thanks.

603
00:37:06,470 --> 00:37:09,780
A girl by herself this late?
You must be lonely, huh?

604
00:37:09,780 --> 00:37:11,600
Who even are you? What do you want?

605
00:37:11,600 --> 00:37:12,430
Let's get some food.

606
00:37:12,430 --> 00:37:14,150
No. I said I don't need it.

607
00:37:15,510 --> 00:37:16,340
Who the heck are you?

608
00:37:19,180 --> 00:37:20,430
Got some nerve, huh?

609
00:37:20,510 --> 00:37:21,740
Out here acting like a creep?

610
00:37:22,220 --> 00:37:22,910
Scram.

611
00:37:27,070 --> 00:37:28,110
You okay, girl?

612
00:37:29,700 --> 00:37:30,510
I'm fine.

613
00:37:31,070 --> 00:37:32,630
Thanks.

614
00:37:32,780 --> 00:37:33,860
No need to thank me.

615
00:37:35,180 --> 00:37:36,470
What's wrong? Lost something?

616
00:37:36,630 --> 00:37:39,380
Yeah, I think I left my phone inside.

617
00:37:39,430 --> 00:37:40,220
It's here?

618
00:37:40,470 --> 00:37:40,820
Yeah.

619
00:37:40,990 --> 00:37:42,150
Alright, no biggie then.

620
00:37:42,840 --> 00:37:44,590
I'll clear the place out
and find it for you.

621
00:37:44,590 --> 00:37:45,550
We'll definitely get it.

622
00:37:47,780 --> 00:37:49,150
That punk hurt you, didn't he?

623
00:37:56,560 --> 00:37:57,860
Still, I can't totally blame him.

624
00:38:00,300 --> 00:38:02,550
You're honestly really pretty.

625
00:38:04,640 --> 00:38:05,630
Don't be scared. Come on.

626
00:38:05,820 --> 00:38:06,590
We'll find your phone.

627
00:38:06,590 --> 00:38:07,110
Let's go. Don't worry.

628
00:38:07,110 --> 00:38:08,380
People are like that.

629
00:38:09,260 --> 00:38:12,030
The more you want something,
the less you get it.

630
00:38:12,950 --> 00:38:16,260
And the more you can't get it,
the more you crave it.

631
00:38:19,030 --> 00:38:20,070
I couldn't figure it out.

632
00:38:23,070 --> 00:38:24,220
What are you doing?

633
00:38:24,560 --> 00:38:25,700
I already made myself clear.

634
00:38:25,700 --> 00:38:27,150
We're over. It's done.

635
00:38:27,950 --> 00:38:30,780
It felt like I was stuck in a loop.

636
00:38:31,740 --> 00:38:33,590
Like there was no way out.

637
00:38:35,110 --> 00:38:36,380
Even after I got sick,

638
00:38:36,950 --> 00:38:38,260
I couldn't figure it out.

639
00:38:39,700 --> 00:38:41,430
When I was in the hospital

640
00:38:42,780 --> 00:38:44,700
they said it was appendicitis.

641
00:38:46,510 --> 00:38:49,180
How did it turn into
that cursed disease because of him?

642
00:38:55,630 --> 00:38:57,110
I didn't tell a soul.

643
00:38:59,860 --> 00:39:02,430
I was in the hospital,
dazed and alone.

644
00:39:03,990 --> 00:39:05,180
And I kept thinking

645
00:39:07,340 --> 00:39:08,740
