646
00:39:09,780 --> 00:39:11,740
But then, the school found out.

647
00:39:12,150 --> 00:39:13,660
They gave me so much encouragement.

648
00:39:13,990 --> 00:39:16,070
It helped me get back on my feet.

649
00:39:19,110 --> 00:39:20,110
And later on,

650
00:39:21,220 --> 00:39:22,630
