This one.

683
00:40:51,860 --> 00:40:52,760
It really looks good.

684
00:40:52,760 --> 00:40:53,150
Let's go.

685
00:40:53,150 --> 00:40:54,070
How much was it again?

686
00:40:54,070 --> 00:40:55,150
Ah, forget it.

687
00:40:55,150 --> 00:40:56,220
Yeah, never mind.

688
