Mom and Dad love me too.

694
00:41:16,150 --> 00:41:17,960
Just like they love Qing and Yu.

695
00:41:19,300 --> 00:41:20,220
Have another piece.

696
00:41:22,740 --> 00:41:23,430
Your hair.

697
00:41:23,475 --> 00:41:27,087
♪I'd still shed tears♪

698
